to build the container:
docker build -t markymo5115/my-django:1.0.0 .

to run the container:
docker run --publish 8000:8080 --detach --name working-django markymo5115/my-django:1.0.0

go to localhost:8000 to see the django default screen

to clean-up
docker stop working-django
docker rm working-django
